parameters: \nc<Saki>Yes, I've been caught up until now...

\nc<Senpai>I was just about to head back, so I can give you a ride on
my way.

\bustMsgExp[1, 4]\nc<Saki>Eh, really!? Thank you so much!\bustMsgExp[1, 2]Um,
Senpai...

\nc<Senpai>Hm? Did he say something to you? Don't worry. We succubi
don't get pregnant unless we want to.

\nc<Saki>(So, that's how it is... I'm relieved.\bustMsgExp[1, 0]Come
to think of it, the company never mentioned anything about
contraception before.)

\nc<Senpai>If you're worried, I'll make sure to provide you with the
proper medication. You're a valuable employee to us, after
all.

\bustMsgExp[1, 2]\nc<Saki>(Even though she's concerned about me, I can't feel
grateful...)

\nc<Senpai>Oh, and getting pregnant would mean you'd be dispatched to
the factory, so be careful.

\nc<Senpai>Of course not. That's why you mustn't get pregnant by
mistake.
